        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="d1e29098" xml:id="d1e165918">Bernardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e165920" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Monte Barro</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324447" xml:id="d1e165923" corresp="Époisses (Côte-d'Or, Semur-en-Auxois)">Espissie</placeName>
                        dominus</persName>, omnibus notum facio <app>
                        <lem>presentibus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#a">pręsentibus</rdg>
                    </app> et futuris quod pie memorie <persName key="d1e29105" xml:id="d1e165933">Heluydis mater mea</persName> in obitu suo dedit in puram <app>
                        <lem>elemosinam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#a">eleemosynam</rdg>
                    </app> ecclesie et fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e165942" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                    <num>x</num> sextarios bladi medietatem frumenti et medietatem avene ad mensuram
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324447" xml:id="d1e165948" corresp="Époisses (Côte-d'Or, Semur-en-Auxois)">Espissie</placeName>
                    singulis annis in terris de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325252" xml:id="d1e165951" corresp="Corseinz">
                        <foreign>Corseinz</foreign>
                    </placeName> circa festum sancti Remigii capiendos. Dedit etiam jamdicte
                    ecclesie fratribus <app>
                        <lem>
                            <num>xx</num>
                        </lem>
                        <rdg wit="#a">viginti</rdg>
                    </app> solidos censuales, scilicet in terra de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325045" xml:id="d1e165962" corresp="Vasseio">Vasseio</placeName> et in terra de capite suo ad
                    jamdictum festum sancti Remigii annuatim persolvendos. Hanc autem <app>
                        <lem>elemosinam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#a">eleemosynam</rdg>
                    </app> venerabilis matris mee laudavi et concessi supradictis fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e165971" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> et in perpetuam
                    memoriam presenti <app>
                        <lem>paginulle</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#a">paginulæ</rdg>
                    </app> sigillum meum apposui, anno Incarnationis dominice <num>m° cc°
                    x°</num>.</p>
